title: Volcom Snowboarding | #IP3 | Teaser
description:

Following up on last year's immensely successful and creative "#IP2" series, Volcom has once again partnered with SNOWBOARDER for the next installment of rider-produced videos, aptly named, "#IP3". Over the next few months, expect to see an eclectic barrage of edits from the stacked Volcom ranks.
